# Control-plane FLEET DEFAULTS — sourced by `dispatch` before the per-repo file.
#
# OPERATOR config: copy to ~/.config/agent-runner/defaults.conf on the executor.
# This is NOT version-controlled with any product repo. Plain shell so the
# viktor-side dispatch needs no toolchain (viktor has no Node on the executor).
#
# A per-repo repos/<name>.conf overrides any of these.
#
# This holds only the MACHINE binding. How to drive the agent (assistant, model,
# effort) lives in each repo's .agent/config.json (versioned with the code); role
# is per-dispatch and defaults to dev (`dispatch <repo> --loop qa` to override).

BASE_BRANCH="master"               # used by dispatch to refresh the runner code
PROXY="http://127.0.0.1:3128"      # the egress proxy the agent uid is locked to
